DISCLAIMER
================================================================================

RalphGuard is a screening tool that uses computational (in-silico) models to
estimate the irritation and toxicity potential of chemical substances.

THE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND. THE AUTHORS
AND COPYRIGHT HOLDERS MAKE NO REPRESENTATIONS OR WARRANTIES REGARDING THE
ACCURACY, COMPLETENESS, OR FITNESS FOR ANY PARTICULAR PURPOSE OF THE
PREDICTIONS GENERATED BY THIS SOFTWARE.

RalphGuard is NOT intended to:
  - Replace standard laboratory testing
  - Replace expert evaluation by toxicologists or formulators
  - Certify product safety for regulatory compliance
  - Provide medical advice or be used with patient data

Users assume full responsibility for any decisions made based on output
from this software.

